## Development Guidelines
- Use TypeScript for all components with proper typing
- Follow React hooks best practices
- Use CSS modules (`.module.scss` or `.module.css`) for styling components
- Organize SCSS files by component or feature for maintainability
- Prefer BEM or similar naming conventions for class names in SCSS
- **Keep SOLID principles** (Single Responsibility, Open/Closed, Liskov Substitution, Interface Segregation, Dependency Inversion) in all code and architecture decisions
- Ensure accessibility with proper ARIA labels and keyboard navigation
- Maintain responsive design principles

- Keep components modular and reusable